00:37:33,496 --> 00:37:37,483
Yeah, yours is to basically
hook me around the throat,

00:37:37,483 --> 00:37:38,493
and--and...
(Laughter)

00:37:38,493 --> 00:37:40,469
So I'm very clear
about that.

00:37:40,469 --> 00:37:42,470
I've been around a long time,
my friend.

00:37:42,470 --> 00:37:43,475
I've seen these fads
come and go, and I'm not saying

00:37:43,475 --> 00:37:46,470
this will go soon,
but I don't know.

00:37:46,470 --> 00:37:48,467
So I'm reflecting it
in the offer.

00:37:48,467 --> 00:37:49,489
He's taking out
his risk screening in the--

00:37:49,489 --> 00:37:51,487
in the form of 40%
of your company.

00:37:51,487 --> 00:37:53,474
If you succeed,
that's a whole lot.

00:37:53,474 --> 00:37:55,484
So have some respect for money.

00:37:55,484 --> 00:37:57,478
Well, no,
and I-I-I appreciate it.

00:37:57,478 --> 00:37:59,487
I've done it my way.
Robert's done it his way.

00:37:59,487 --> 00:38:01,472
Now go make a decision.
Okay.

00:38:01,472 --> 00:38:03,468
Thank you.
I'll be right back.

00:38:05,480 --> 00:38:07,469
I think you're asking
for too much.

00:38:07,469 --> 00:38:08,491
We gotta get some cash
along the way.

00:38:08,491 --> 00:38:12,471
Come into my deal, and I'll drop
the royalty in perpetuity

00:38:12,471 --> 00:38:14,491
down to 40 cents,
but I'm keeping it a buck 10.

00:38:14,491 --> 00:38:16,477
I like the fact you're
getting cash along the way.

00:38:16,477 --> 00:38:18,469
Yes.

00:38:18,469 --> 00:38:21,488
Uh, Mr. wonderful offered me
a deal that wasn't so wonderful.

00:38:21,488 --> 00:38:25,484
(Chuckles)
Uh, as far as a royalty that
exceeds the cost of the product,

00:38:25,484 --> 00:38:26,494
uh, but no equity.

00:38:26,494 --> 00:38:31,492
And then, um, Robert offered me
40% of the company,

00:38:31,492 --> 00:38:33,485
which just is outrageous.

00:38:33,485 --> 00:38:36,492
Kevin, let's lower
the dollar amount per product

00:38:36,492 --> 00:38:39,469
and lower the equity.
Okay, we're gonna drop it down
to 70 cents?

00:38:39,469 --> 00:38:41,488
Let's take it to 25% equity
and lower it to 75 cents.

00:38:41,488 --> 00:38:43,489
Okay, and what's
the perpetual royalty?

00:38:43,489 --> 00:38:46,484
Is that gonna be--
there's no perpetual royalty?

00:38:46,484 --> 00:38:48,469
Well, that's the equity.
Right. No, no--

00:38:48,469 --> 00:38:50,469
the equity--
you want the equity
and you want the royalty.

00:38:50,469 --> 00:38:52,467
Yeah. I think
there's a lesson.

